  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA29">
<l>iṟaiyu nilaṉu miruvicumpuṅ kāṟṟu</l>
<l>maṟaipuṉaluñ centīyu māvāṉ – piṟaimaruppiṟ</l>
<l>paiṅkaṇmāl yāṉai paṭutuyaraṅ kāttaḷitta</l>
<l>ceṅkaṇmāl kaṇṭāy teḷi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord, the ground, the dark sky, the wind,</l>
<l>the dashing flood, and the red fire is he. See red-eyed Māl,</l>
<l>who warded off with care the misery suffered by the green-eyed</l> 
<l>big elephant with crescent tusks, [and] understand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
